name: Ricky Powell [photo by eklektic]
description:
shot July 14, 2007 in The Village.

Ricky Powell is a street photographer and host of the public access show, Rappin' with the Rickster. He has a column in Mass Appeal Magazine called "Ricky Powell is... the Doloist". He was crowned "the Weegee of hiphop" by Fab 5 Freddy and immortalized in the Beastie Boys song, Car Thief

July 14, 2007
